ec7f0b08847b7","tid":949923,"uid":18955,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"Chinese Navy Is The Best?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"China Navy is the best joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35af2079c7e56040d0174620fd45ed0f3432b34e","tid":949923,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係等你起到第十架先冧你咩⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447923ccc7e457fa828c102e9c5cac3cdb07936a","tid":949923,"uid":71185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"其實共狗知唔知航母係要有好多戰艦組成戰鬥群先有用？否則只係一個移動箭靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbac0c8b39de623c302c59af5c962611d9a3402","tid":949923,"uid":52068,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國大陸為何堅持不肯放棄台灣，其中一大原因就是戰略位置。中國大陸新浪軍事網今日一篇<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分析文章指出</span></strong></span>，中國海軍未來30年內很<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能</span></span>會擁有10艘航空母艦，還說<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等統一台灣後</span></span>，部屬在台灣海軍基地的航母便能迅速出擊東北亞地區，並隔離駐守在夏威夷美軍。<br />\n <br />\n該篇文章<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">指出</span></strong></span>，中國在10年前<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提出</span></span>建造5艘航母的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標</span></span>。美國有專家指出，種種跡象顯示，「這只不過是才剛剛開始，中國海軍按全球利益來說至少要10艘航母才夠」。文中還<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說</span></span>，西方<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推測</span></span>到2049年，中國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能</span></span>擁有10多艘航母。同時海軍陸戰隊將擴大到10萬人，最終將擁有30至40艘大型兩棲戰艦組成的遠洋海軍。而為了停靠航母，中國海軍也正在大規模興建航母基地。<br />\n <br />\n該文作者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">表示</span></span>，解放軍已經在青島和海南島亞龍灣新建航母基地，能容納4艘航空母艦，加上興城航母基地，最多停靠6艘航母。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作者接著囂張地寫著</span></span>：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果</span></span>統一台灣後，可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想像</span></span>，台灣一些新建的海軍基地和港口，最終可能容納至少8至10艘核動力航空母艦。來自海南和台灣基地的核動力航母戰鬥群可以迅速出擊東北亞，隔離在關島和夏威夷美國海軍部隊，還可前往南太平洋，印度洋，非洲和大西洋。」<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文中還說</span></span>，隨著「一帶一路」計畫執行，中國需要更多的海外基地供軍艦遠航停靠補給。吉布地是中國公開建立的第一個真正的海外基地，除此以外，將來中國可能在柬埔寨、緬甸、斯里蘭卡、巴基斯坦、馬爾地夫、塞席爾、那萬杜、斐濟、聖多美及普林西比島、奈及利亞、尚比亞和委內瑞拉建立類似軍事通道和後勤設施。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">諷刺的是，中國大陸國家主席習近平本周二在中共改革開放40周年大會上還強調中國不想稱霸，但這篇文章卻高調揭露出中國想成海洋霸權的野心。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181221/1487361/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181221%2F1487361%2F&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6a5a3c82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181221%2F1487361%2F&h=dca8459e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181221/1487361/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"637549bbb33b76d7c5f9c0d6cca702e1a72d7cee","tid":949923,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor